body: Perhaps the easiest approach would be to install the current nightly on one of our Windows test VMs, run a modified version of `estimator_test.py` that blocks before the rename, and apply https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/sysinternals/processexplorer.aspx to the Python interpreter to see what handles are open?
